  "title": "🌟 Luxury Retail Supervisor | $3,500 - $4,500 | Orchard",
  "description": "<p>🌟 <strong>Luxury Retail Supervisor</strong> 🌟<br /><br />💰 <strong>Salary: $3,500 – $4,500</strong><br />📍 <strong>Location: Orchard Road</strong><br /></p><p>Step into the world of luxury retail and lead a premium shopping experience in the heart of Orchard. We are looking for a confident and service-driven <strong>Luxury Retail Supervisor</strong> to inspire the team and deliver exceptional customer experiences.</p><h3>✨ <strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Supervise daily store operations to ensure smooth and efficient performance</p></li><li><p>Lead, motivate, and coach retail associates to achieve sales targets and service excellence</p></li><li><p>Deliver personalised, high-touch customer service aligned with luxury brand standards</p></li><li><p>Handle customer enquiries, feedback, and escalations professionally</p></li><li><p>Monitor sales performance, KPIs, and inventory levels</p></li><li><p>Support visual merchandising and ensure store presentation meets brand guidelines</p></li></ul><h3>👤 <strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Minimum<strong> 3-5 years of retail experience i</strong>n <strong>luxury or premium brands</strong></p></li><li><p>Prior <strong>supervisory or team-leading experience</strong></p></li><li><p>Strong communication and interpersonal skills</p></li><li><p>Customer-centric mindset with a passion for luxury retail</p></li><li><p>Well-groomed, professional, and confident personality</p></li><li><p>Able to work retail hours, including weekends and public holidays</p></li></ul><h3>🎁 <strong>What’s in It for You</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Competitive salary package <strong>($3,500 – $4,500)</strong></p></li><li><p>Prime working location at <strong>Orchard Road</strong></p></li><li><p>Career progression opportunities within luxury retail</p></li><li><p>Work with premium products in an elegant retail environment<br /><br /><br /><strong>📩 Apply Now</strong></p><p>Submit your resume to</p><p>📧 Email : annabelle.koh@crew.sg</p><p>📱 WhatsApp : 80882564<br /></p><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.<br /></p><p>Annabelle Koh (R25158748)</p><p>Hrnet Ventures Pte Ltd - Crew by Hrnet</p><p>E.A.24C2435</p></li></ul>",
